We’re hosting a Diwali party on Saturday, 25th October, at an Airbnb venue! ✨
It’ll be a traditional-themed evening filled with good vibes, great food, and festive fun.

Let’s celebrate the festival of lights together and make some amazing memories.
If you’re interested in joining, please DM us, and I’ll add you to the group for all the details.

