Our very own DTU&#39;s official Pokémon community is finally here, and every Pokéfan is invited, whether old or new! 🎉

We&#39;ll definitely make it worth your time! You will get to:

• Meet fellow trainers and have Pokémon battles 💥
• Participate in Pokémon quizzes and win free official merch! 🧠
• Enjoy Pokémon GO! community events 🎮
• Participate in and win VGC events organised within campus

We are excited to welcome each and every one of you and, whether it&#39;s for a trip down memory lane or for an eager and energetic hardcore Pokémon battle, there&#39;s something for everyone!

Join using the link below to begin your very own Pokémon journey at DTU!🚀

