We'll definitely make it worth your time! You will get to:

• Meet fellow trainers and have Pokémon battles <img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="💥" draggable="false" class="b71 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -60px -80px;">
• Participate in Pokémon quizzes and win free official merch! <img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🧠" draggable="false" class="b128 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -40px -40px;">
• Enjoy Pokémon GO! community events <img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🎮" draggable="false" class="b27 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -60px -20px;">
• Participate in and win VGC events organised within campus

We are excited to welcome each and every one of you and, whether it's for a trip down memory lane or for an eager and energetic hardcore Pokémon battle, there's something for everyone!

Join using the link below to begin your very own Pokémon journey at DTU!<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🚀" draggable="false" class="b88 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -80px -80px;">

