With a heavy heart, we regret to inform you that GROOVE’26 stands cancelled due to unforeseen administrative shortcomings.

We understand that many of you had invested your time, effort, and enthusiasm in preparing for the competitions, and we sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused. 
Your participation and trust meant a lot to us.

This is not the outcome we had envisioned, but some circumstances remain beyond control.

That said, what we built through GROOVE goes beyond a single event. The energy, ambition, and spirit of this community will continue.

We will come back stronger.

Thank you for your support and understanding.

Warm regards,
Team Business Bulls‬"><div class="x1c4vz4f x3nfvp2 xuce83p x1bft6iq x1i7k8ik xq9mrsl x6s0dn4"><div class="x78zum5"><span dir="auto" aria-label="Maybe Siddharth Jain" class="x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">~ Siddharth Jain</span></div></div><span>:&nbsp;</span><span dir="ltr" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">Dear Participants&nbsp;

With a heavy heart, we regret to inform you that GROOVE’26 stands cancelled due to unforeseen administrative shortcomings.

We understand that many of you had invested your time, effort, and enthusiasm in preparing for the competitions, and we sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused.&nbsp;
Your participation and trust meant a lot to us.

This is not the outcome we had envisioned, but some circumstances remain beyond control.

That said, what we built through GROOVE goes beyond a single event. The energy, ambition, and spirit of this community will continue.

We will come back stronger.

Thank you for your support and understanding.

Warm regards,
Team Business Bulls</span></span></div><div role="gridcell" aria-colindex="1" class="_ak8i"><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="x10l6tqk xh8yej3 x1g42fcv" role="row" style="z-index: 486; transition: none; height: 95px; transform: translateY(1748px);"><div role="gridcell" class="x1n2onr6" tabindex="0"><div tabindex="-1" class="" aria-selected="false"><div class="_ak72 false false false _ak73 _ak7n _asiw _am_1 _ap1- _ap1_"><div class="_ak8n"><div class="_ak8h"><div class="x1n2onr6 x78zum5 x1q0g3np x15jighw x112a4uq"><div class="x1n2onr6 x1f2iure x1bczwif x17un8ov x1e7945m x11o6v7j" style="height: 31px; width: 31px;"><div class="x1n2onr6 xh8yej3 x5yr21d x1f2iure"><img alt="" draggable="false" class="x1n2onr6 x1lliihq xh8yej3 x5yr21d x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xl1xv1r x115dhu7 x17vty23 x1f2iure x1bczwif x17un8ov x1e7945m x11o6v7j x1hc1fzr _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="./wish_files/file(20).enc" style="visibility: visible;"><svg class="x10l6tqk x13vifvy x1o0tod xh8yej3 x5yr21d x47corl" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="100,50 100,56.6 100,59.3 100,61.4 99.9,63.2 99.9,64.8 99.9,66.2 99.8,67.5 99.8,68.7 99.7,69.8 99.6,70.8 99.5,71.8 99.5,72.8 99.4,73.7 99.3,74.6 99.1,75.4 99,76.3 98.9,77 98.8,77.8 98.6,78.5 98.5,79.2 98.3,79.9 98.1,80.6 98,81.3 97.8,81.9 97.6,82.5 97.4,83.1 97.2,83.7 97,84.3 96.8,84.8 96.5,85.4 96.3,85.9 96,86.4 95.8,86.9 95.5,87.4 95.3,87.9 95,88.3 94.7,88.8 94.4,89.2 94.1,89.7 93.8,90.1 93.4,90.5 93.1,90.9 92.8,91.3 92.4,91.7 92,92 91.7,92.4 91.3,92.8 90.9,93.1 90.5,93.4 90.1,93.8 89.7,94.1 89.2,94.4 88.8,94.7 88.3,95 87.9,95.3 87.4,95.5 86.9,95.8 86.4,96 85.9,96.3 85.4,96.5 84.8,96.8 84.3,97 83.7,97.2 83.1,97.4 82.5,97.6 81.9,97.8 81.3,98 80.6,98.1 79.9,98.3 79.2,98.5 78.5,98.6 77.8,98.8 77,98.9 76.3,99 75.4,99.1 74.6,99.3 73.7,99.4 72.8,99.5 71.8,99.5 70.8,99.6 69.8,99.7 68.7,99.8 67.5,99.8 66.2,99.9 64.8,99.9 63.2,99.9 6